channel.title: 194 Mapdata
channel.description:
[center]I'm looking for a download of the original [i]194[/i] map data or complete cache.
It's next to impossible to find considering it was over five years ago. Please reply and keep this thread alive until it's found! Thank you very much.

item.title: 194 Mapdata
item.dc:creator: @glestrts glestrts
item.description:
@glestrts wrote:

[quote=“Rixxx, post:6, topic:322415”][quote author=glestrts link=topic=418810.msg3078491#msg3078491 date=1262012488]
he has the deob and cache, he just needs the 194 mapdata…

ill ask peterbjornx
[/quote]

He said he was also looking for a complete cache. Learn to read.[/quote]
I gave him the 194 client and the cache is complete for the time, except for the mapdata which was never released with the cache because it was glitched (like 474-499, no map objects), and now so many years later it is nearly impossible to get ahold of unless you have an old hard drive from 03 that crashed during rs beta.

Next time at least try to pretend to know what your talking about.
